<h3>🚀 Your Account Activation Steps:</h3>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Check Your Email (Within 5 Minutes)</strong>
    - Look for "Set Up Your DonorLens Account" with a secure password setup
    link.</li>
  <li><strong>Click the Setup Link</strong>
    - The link expires in 24 hours and can only be used once for security.</li>
  <li><strong>Verify Your Identity</strong>
    - Enter your email address and NGO registration number to confirm identity.</li>
  <li><strong>Create Your Password</strong>
    - Set a strong, secure password (minimum 8 characters).</li>
  <li><strong>Start Making Impact!</strong>
    - Login to your dashboard and begin creating campaigns!</li>
</ul>

